# **Boba Haven**

## **Acceptance Criteria**

    When the page loads
    Then user will see a homepage displaying all the drinks
    When the user signs up
    Then there will be a profile page for them also giving them access to order drinks
    When one of the drinks are chosen
    Then the drink page will be displayed giving the user 3 sizes to choose from
    When the user chooses a size before adding to cart
    Then it adds the drink to the shopping cart
    When the user clicks on the shopping cart
    Then all the drinks are displayed 
    When the final checkout button is clicked
    Then the user is promted to put in credit card information
    When the form is filled out 
    Then the user will be notifed their purchase was accepted

## **Description**

This app was created to streamline receiving orders and payment. This should allow the baristas to focus on making the dirnks as they come in and should lessen the wait for when the customers come in ready for their order to be ready.


## **Getting Started**

If you clone the repo follow the steps below:
- open the terminal for the project
- run 'npm run i' to install the dependencies
- fill out the .env example files
- run 'npm run seed'
- run 'npm run develop'

After the app starts running if you don't want to login we have a preset test login that you are open to use  

email: test123@gmail.com  

password: password01

